{{BLP unsourced|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}} '''Perla Farías Lombardini''' is a Venezuelan television director, producer, screenwriter, and an executive at [[Telemundo]]. She is the daughter of actress Gioia Lombardini, and director Daniel Farías.
